com.i2group.apollo.commandservice.transport.ICommand

Packages that use ICommand
com.i2group.apollo.commandservice.transport Contains classes and interfaces for commands that make changes to data in the Analysis Repository.

Subinterfaces of ICommand in com.i2group.apollo.commandservice.transport
 interface IItemChangeSetCommand
          A command that makes changes to the Cards of an Item.
